### =====================================================================
### Ipg API  (base route: api/Ipg/)
### Pay = POST (JSON). Gateway & Verify are GET pages used by the payment flow.
### =====================================================================
@host = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = your-dev-api-key
@token =

### Pay - open the gateway, returns a url to show in a WebView
POST {{host}}/api/Ipg/Pay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "amount": 150000
}

### Gateway - test-only fake gateway page (GET). Opened by Pay in test mode.
GET {{host}}/api/Ipg/Gateway?additionalData=SOME_DATA&amount=150000

### Verify - callback (GET). Normally the gateway redirects here; shown for reference.
GET {{host}}/api/Ipg/Verify?additionalData=SOME_DATA&token=FAKE&status=0&rrn=123456789&cardNumberMasked=627412******2424
